'''豆蟹'''（''Pinnotheres pisum''）是[[豆蟹屬|豆蟹屬]]的一種小型螃蟹，寄生在牡蠣和其他一些[[双壳纲|双壳纲]]生物身上。它單純依靠這些寄主爲生，並可能對寄主造成損害<ref name="Berrill">{{cite book |author=N. J. Berrill & Jacquelyn Berrill |title=1001 Questions Answered About the Seashore |location=New York |year=1957 |publisher=[[Dover_Publications|Dover Publications]] |isbn=0-486-23366-9}}</ref>。這種螃蟹因爲只有豌豆那麽大而得名，實際上其种加詞的意思就是豌豆。其雄蟹螯比雌性長，背殼也更堅硬，雌性的背殼呈透明狀，可看到體内器官<ref name="Ingle">{{cite book |author=Ray W. Ingle |title=Crayfishes, Lobsters, and Crabs of Europe: An Illustrated Guide to Common and Traded Species |location=London |publisher=[[Chapman_&_Hall|Chapman & Hall]] |year=1997 |isbn=978-0-412-71060-5}}</ref>。

== 繁殖==
[[File:Parasite140113-mov1-olm_Pea_crab_Nepinnotheres_novaezelandiae_in_mussel.ogv|thumb]]
雄性豆蟹在交配期會花數小時摩擦藏有雌蟹的貝殼，直到貝殼打開<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/05/150508-crabs-tickle-shellfish-science-animals-new-zealand |title=Nationalgeographic.com 2015-05-08 Crab Tickles Shellfish for Hours to Find Love |accessdate=2018-02-12 |archive-date=2017-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216201139/https://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/05/150508-crabs-tickle-shellfish-science-animals-new-zealand/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[奧克蘭大學|奧克蘭大學]]的研究者發現''[[Nepinnotheres_novaezelandiae|Nepinnotheres novaezelandiae]]''也有同樣的行爲模式。<ref name="TrottierJeffs2015">{{cite journal|last1=Trottier|first1=Oliver|last2=Jeffs|first2=Andrew G.|title=Mate locating and access behaviour of the parasitic pea crab, ''Nepinnotheres novaezelandiae'', an important parasite of the mussel ''Perna canaliculus''|journal=Parasite|volume=22|year=2015|pages=13|issn=1776-1042|doi=10.1051/parasite/2015013|pmid=25786327|pmc=4365294}} {{open access}}</ref>

